WEBVTT

1
01:37:27.960 --> 01:37:30.870 
拉夫克鲁什卡的离去
Rav Krushka's departure

2
01:37:31.760 --> 01:37:33.190 
让我们
leaves us

3
01:37:34.560 --> 01:37:36.270 
面对着空虚
facing a void,

4
01:37:37.560 --> 01:37:38.750 
不知所措
bewildered.

5
01:37:40.520 --> 01:37:41.550 
今日
Today,

6
01:37:42.840 --> 01:37:44.950 
令我们宽慰的是知道
we take comfort in knowing

7
01:37:45.040 --> 01:37:48.950 
他的遗产将得以保存
that his legacy will be preserved

8
01:37:49.040 --> 01:37:52.110 
并且延续到下一代
and carried through to the next generation.

